## Radius & Animations

- **Radius base**:
  - `--radius: 0.25rem;`
  - Derived radii: `--radius-xs`, `--radius-sm`, `--radius-md`, `--radius-lg`, `--radius-xl`, `--radius-2xl`, `--radius-3xl`, `--radius-4xl`.
- **Named animations** (use via Tailwind or `var(--animate-...)`):
  - `--animate-slide-up` → `slideUp 0.2s ease-out;`
  - `--animate-slide-down` → `slideDown 0.2s ease-out;`
  - `--animate-marquee-x` → `marqueeX var(--marquee-duration) ...;`
  - `--animate-marquee-y` → `marqueeY var(--marquee-duration) ...;`

---

## Shark UI–specific Practices

- **Theme components**: keep components inside theme folders (`app/themes/_components/...`) cohesive and reusable.
- **Tokens before magic values**: always try theme variables and utilities before hardcoded values (`#fff`, `16px`, etc.).
- **Consistency over preference**: when adding new code, copy structural and visual patterns from existing components in the project.
